This repository contains JSON mod files for the game Crimson Desert.

The mod files are derivative works of original mods authored by:
- lemonheads / CyberGecko1 (Infinite Stamina, Infinite Spirit and Spirit Regen)
- Pldada / PLMOST (EasyMoney, Craft GoldBar With 1 GoldOre)

The byte-offset rebasing work for game version 1.04.02 was performed by Bloodawn,
and the rebased files are released under the same terms (or stricter terms) as
the original mods they derive from. Where original mods include redistribution
restrictions in their readme.txt, those restrictions still apply.

This is a community fan-modding effort with no commercial intent. No claim is
made to ownership of Crimson Desert game assets, file formats, or intellectual
property. "Crimson Desert" is a trademark of Pearl Abyss.

If you are an original mod author and want your work removed from this
repository, please open an issue or contact the maintainer and it will be
removed promptly.

Original mods can be found on Nexus Mods at:
- https://www.nexusmods.com/crimsondesert/mods/107  (lemonheads stamina)
- https://www.nexusmods.com/crimsondesert/mods/135  (lemonheads spirit)
- https://www.nexusmods.com/crimsondesert/mods/917  (Pldada EasyMoney)
- https://www.nexusmods.com/crimsondesert/mods/1100 (Pldada Craft GoldBar)

The rebasing methodology, scripts, and documentation in this repository
(excluding the JSON mod files themselves and any text quoted from original
mods' readmes) are released under the MIT License:

